WEBVTT

00:03.229 --> 00:04.890
<i>Previously on</i> Hawaii Five-O...

00:04.990 --> 00:06.555
Who are you?
I'm Marco Reyes.

00:06.557 --> 00:09.324
When your brother disappeared,
he was in possession

00:09.326 --> 00:11.216
<i>of a significant amount</i>
<i>of my money.</i>

00:11.218 --> 00:13.652
$18½ million.

00:13.654 --> 00:16.018
You have until Monday to bring
my money to this address.

00:16.020 --> 00:17.619
What happens if I don't
bring you the money?

00:17.621 --> 00:19.217
You'll get a package with
your brother's head in it.

00:19.219 --> 00:23.188
<i> Reyes said that Matty</i>
<i>owed him $18½ million.</i>

00:23.190 --> 00:26.787
You see, this is only
$13 million.

00:26.789 --> 00:27.723
Are you sure?

00:27.725 --> 00:28.725
Yes, I am positive.

00:28.726 --> 00:29.827
I counted it three times.

00:29.829 --> 00:33.218
And now I am, uh,
$5½ million short,

00:33.220 --> 00:35.948
and I have two days to come up
with all of it,

00:35.950 --> 00:38.179
or, um, my brother's dead.

00:38.181 --> 00:40.141
I really don't see any other ways.
I may have one.

00:40.142 --> 00:41.969
Maybe we can do
a little quid pro quo.

00:41.971 --> 00:43.638
Tell me what you want.

00:43.640 --> 00:46.038
Immediate transfer
to the special holding unit

00:46.040 --> 00:47.342
at the high-security facility.

00:47.344 --> 00:49.674
There I'll get a private cell,
and for that

00:49.676 --> 00:50.769
I am willing to pay...

00:50.771 --> 00:52.504
$5½ million.

00:52.506 --> 00:54.006
This is gonna cost you

00:54.008 --> 00:56.740
in ways that you could not
possibly predict.

00:56.742 --> 00:58.569
It's all there, okay?

00:58.571 --> 01:00.838
Just, uh, let me
see my brother now.

01:00.840 --> 01:02.604
Hey, Matty. Matty.

01:08.904 --> 01:10.569
Look at me, look at me.

